OL,6,FJersey politicians have voted to
OL,7,Fbolster the rights of renters in
OL,8,Flandmark changes to the island's
OL,9,Ftenancy law.
OL,11,FDeputy Sam Mezec, Jersey's Housing
OL,12,FMinister, proposed several measures to
OL,13,Fimprove the rights of renters, which
OL,14,Fhe hopes will make "responsibilities
OL,15,Fand obligations of landlords and
OL,16,Ftenants much clearer".
OL,18,FThe Minister has previously said the
OL,19,Fchanges would "alleviate the housing
OL,20,Fcrisis" on the island.
