OL,6,FWhile Deputy Mezec has had to accept
OL,7,Famendments to his proposition -such as
OL,8,Fdropping his plan for a 5% cap on rent
OL,9,Fincreases - States Members have agreed
OL,10,Fto most of his proposed changes to the
OL,11,FResidential Tenancy (Jersey) Law 2011.
OL,13,FThe changes include:
OL,15,FDeputy Mezec says he was "delighted"
OL,16,Fwith the changes, which he says will
OL,17,F"improve the protections afforded to
OL,18,Frenters and landlords in Jersey".
