OL,3,CMove to ban revenge evictions and
OL,4,Climit rent increases approved
OL,6,FHe explains: "Renters will benefit
OL,7,Ffrom protection against unfair rent
OL,8,Fhikes above RPI, and they will no
OL,9,Flonger need to feel afraid to raise a
OL,10,Fconcern with their landlord, with the
OL,11,Frisk of being served notice in revenge
OL,12,Fbeing closed out by new, legally
OL,13,Fdefined reasons to end a tenancy.
OL,15,F"I will now be turning my attention to
OL,16,Fbringing the laws to life for
OL,17,Fislanders as quickly as possible.
