OL,6,F"Additional legislation will be
OL,7,Fprogressed to step-up the Rent
OL,8,FTribunal and recruit members, and I
OL,9,Falso want to ensure high-quality
OL,10,Fguidance is available to support
OL,11,Fislanders in a seamless transition to
OL,12,Fthe new Law, in due course.
OL,14,F"I will be continuing to work
